Hi folks, I suggest that you add a way to label multiple attachments at once, without having to click into each attachment manually to add labels.

This could be useful because when users upload images, it often makes  sense to bulk label them so that they can be found later and used in image macros which rely on labels.

For example in a series of five images, all of them might receive the "bridge" label, and three of them might also receive a "repairs" label. With the current interface, labeling the images accordingly would take approximately five minutes, whereas a bulk editor might allow this to be done within seconds.

